                      "value": "alternative"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "value": " may be used in the deprecation message to insert the name of an alternative to the deprecated function. "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "inlineCode",
                      "value": "obj_type"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "value": " may be used to insert a friendly name for the type of object being deprecated."
